Booking - Class in application.models
Purpose: Booking class containing fields and methods pertaining to a single booking Description: Contains information about the booking in the form of String fields, and a list of seats for the Booking (note: unlike the one in Screening, the seats list in Booking does not contain information about any unbooked seats; there are no false values in the HashMap
Booking(String, LocalDateTime, String, HashMap<String, Boolean>) - Constructor for class application.models.Booking
Constructor Sets the Booking's film title, dateTime, seats, and username of the Customer that made the Booking from the parameters; constructs a bookingID from the dateTime and the username.
Booking(JSONObject) - Constructor for class application.models.Booking
Constructor Given a JSONObject, sets the fields of the Booking object based on the corresponding key-value pairs in the JSONObject; parses the JSONObject and calls the constructor above.
BookingController - Class in application.controllers
Purpose: Display Booking information, and manipulate Booking objects Description: Contains all methods manipulating bookings, and sets up the views primarily governed with booking tables and manipulation (Booking (for displaying information about a particular booking), Bookings (for displaying a table of all bookings a Customer has made), BookingSeats (for displaying a seat plan a Customer can choose their booking seats from), and Screening (for displaying an employee a seat plan for a screening, and enabling the employee to delete the screening)).
